      <description></description>
      
      <content>&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m Noam Elfanbaum, I live in Tel-Aviv with my wife, baby-daughter and dog.
I used to teach Python classes, do freelance work and organize Python community gatherings (&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.meetup.com/PyWeb-IL/&#34;&gt;PywebIL&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://il.pycon.org&#34;&gt;Pycon Israel&lt;/a&gt;). These days I&#39;ve settled on a serious day job as a engineering team lead a Bluevine. Hope you enjoy the blog posts!&lt;/p&gt;
